      },
      {
        "start": "03:04.400",
        "end": "03:05.100",
        "original": "ぱぴぷぺぽ",
        "english": "Pa-pi-pu-pe-po",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:05.100",
        "end": "03:05.900",
        "original": "ぱぴぷぺぽ",
        "english": "Pa-pi-pu-pe-po",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:05.900",
        "end": "03:06.600",
        "original": "ぱぴぷぺぽ",
        "english": "Pa-pi-pu-pe-po",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:07.400",
        "end": "03:08.900",
        "original": "Poppin',",
        "english": "Poppin',",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:08.900",
        "end": "03:10.500",
        "original": "POP!",
        "english": "POP!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:22.000",
        "end": "03:26.000",
        "original": "みんなー！ゲストパートどうだったー？",
        "english": "Everyone! How was the guest part?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:26.000",
        "end": "03:29.000",
        "original": "可愛かった？ありがとうございます。",
        "english": "Was it cute? Thank you very much.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:29.000",
        "end": "03:33.000",
        "original": "ということでね、すごい続けてやってしまったんですが、",
        "english": "So, I did them all in a row,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:33.000",
        "end": "03:39.000",
        "original": "まず「サクラ・アプレシエイション」は、AZKiちゃんとルーナちゃんとリリカに出てもらいました。",
        "english": "First, for 'Sakura Appreciation', I had AZKi-chan, Luna-chan, and Ririka join me.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:39.000",
        "end": "03:45.000",
        "original": "なんかすごい桜というか、春っぽいね、ピンクーな感じのメンバーをね、呼びました。",
        "english": "I invited members who felt very 'cherry blossom' or spring-like, with a pink vibe.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:45.000",
        "end": "03:47.000",
        "original": "リリカすごい頑張ってたよなぁ。",
        "english": "Ririka really worked hard, didn't she?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:47.000",
        "end": "03:54.000",
        "original": "すごいね、練習中も「あー！できないー！」って言いながらね、頑張ってたリリカ。",
        "english": "She was saying 'Ah! I can't do it!' even during practice, but she did her best.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:54.000",
        "end": "03:56.000",
        "original": "そして次「逃げない」ね。",
        "english": "And next, 'Nigenai'.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:56.000",
        "end": "04:00.000",
        "original": "「逃げない」はちょっと結構古めの曲なんですけど、",
        "english": "'Nigenai' is a bit of an older song,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:00.000",
        "end": "04:05.000",
        "original": "まつりがすごーいすごい大好きで一番推していた「ゆるめるモ！」さんの楽曲で、",
        "english": "It's a song by 'Yurumerumo!', who I really love and supported the most,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:05.000",
        "end": "04:10.000",
        "original": "あの、ここで歌えてすごく嬉しかったです。ありがとうございますね。",
        "english": "And I was so happy to be able to sing it here. Thank you.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:10.000",
        "end": "04:14.000",
        "original": "そして「特別して」は、もう難しかった！",
        "english": "And 'Tokubetsu Shite' was just so difficult!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:14.000",
        "end": "04:15.500",
        "original": "すごい難しかったんだから。",
        "english": "It was really hard.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:15.500",
        "end": "04:21.000",
        "original": "だってさ、1番と2番さ、あのサビの振りも違うしさ、めちゃ難しかったよ。",
        "english": "Because the choreography for the chorus is different in the first and second verses, it was super hard.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:21.000",
        "end": "04:27.000",
        "original": "や、=LOVEさんの曲は毎回難しいけど、すごい踊ってて楽しいでございますね。",
        "english": "Well, =LOVE's songs are always difficult, but they're really fun to dance to.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:27.000",
        "end": "04:29.000",
        "original": "はい、そして「ぱぴぷぺPOP!」。",
        "english": "Yes, and 'Papipupe POP!'.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:29.000",
        "end": "04:36.000",
        "original": "これ、あの、ずっとこうやってるからすごい疲れて、あの汗だくになった。",
        "english": "Since I was doing this the whole time, I got really tired and covered in sweat.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:36.000",
        "end": "04:38.000",
        "original": "もうすごかったよ。",
        "english": "It was intense.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:38.000",
        "end": "04:45.000",
        "original": "練習中の時も汗だくすぎて「ちょっと待って、ちょっと疲れた」とか言ってね、",
        "english": "Even during practice, I was sweating so much and saying, 'Wait a sec, I'm a bit tired',",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:45.000",
        "end": "04:50.000",
        "original": "みんなでわちゃわちゃしながらね、練習もしましたけど、すごい楽しかったでございます。",
        "english": "We practiced while messing around together, and it was a lot of fun.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:50.000",
        "end": "04:57.000",
        "original": "そして、ちょっと紹介できてなかったこちらのステージ！じゃーん！可愛いー！",
        "english": "And, this stage that I hadn't introduced yet! Ta-da! It's so cute!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:57.000",
        "end": "05:00.000",
        "original": "すごい可愛くね、作っていただきました。",
        "english": "They made it look very cute for me.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      }
    ],
    "model_name": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
  }
